and should
have, faith that things will be
better.

11:14.974 --> 11:18.278 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Some powerful
voices.

11:18.311 --> 11:23.483 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And next: schoolchildren and how
the combative
political season has affected
them.

11:23.516 --> 11:25.451 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And to Hari Sreenivasan in New
York.

11:25.485 --> 11:29.789 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Teachers and
