happen next.

12:02.088 --> 12:06.225 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JULIAN MASTERS, Student: I'm not
devastated
that Trump is president.

12:06.259 --> 12:09.662 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think it sends a pretty strong
message to
the American people that
something needs to

12:09.696 --> 12:11.097 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
change.

12:11.130 --> 12:15.168 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A vote for Trump doesn't mean
