a racist or anti-woman.

12:15.201 --> 12:18.605 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Maybe the country does need to
be run more
like a business, so we can
actually get things

12:18.638 --> 12:20.506 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
done.

12:20.540 --> 12:24.811 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JESSICA BRUNT, Student: I just
didn't understand
how such a hateful man could
rise to power

12:24.844 --> 12:26.045 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
so quickly.

12:26.079 --> 12:30.249 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I have been really angry,
but now I'm
just tired.

12:30.283 --> 12:33.219 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I'm tired that he is now
state-sponsored.

12:33.252 --> 12:38.191 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SKY ISLAND THOMAS, Student: I
feel like a
lot of students, people in
general, educated

12:38.224 --> 12:43.563 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
themselves through social media
and what was
on television, rather than
informing themselves.

12:43.596 --> 12:48.368 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARTA KIROS, Student: I feel
like, as minorities,
as people of color, at LGBT
community, as

12:48.401 --> 12:54.107 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Muslims, as everyone who has
